US-based model, Morey Faith has offered insights into how to ascertain one’s real relationship status ahead of Valentine’s Day. Morey, while tipping lovers on how to ascertain their position in their partner’s life as the February 14 date approaches, advised this isn’t the best time to pick up a fight with each other.   Wizkid’s song inspired me to do music – Portable     I’ve been depressed for two years – Kida Kudz     Collabo with Olamide has attracted ladies finer than my mom,…   She went on to say as one endeavours to stay in peace with their partner at this time, if your suddenly disappears on Valentine’s Day, it only means you are the side chick/guy. “Ladies/guys, this is not the time to fight with your boo. Valentine’s Day is around the corner. If he or she disappears on that day or gives you a flimsy excuse for not being around, don’t buy it. You’re the side chick/guy,” she wrote.